        <p>Selecting the correct combi boiler size is crucial for ensuring you have adequate heating and hot water in your home. Combi boilers are rated in kilowatts (kW), which indicates their output power. The right size depends on several factors including the number of bedrooms, bathrooms, radiators, and your property's insulation levels.</p>
        
